# ğŸ§  Daily Productivity Assistant

This Python-based assistant helps you manage your personal productivity using:
- Daily planning prompts
- Pomodoro-based work cycles (25+5)
- Cross-platform notifications
- Task completion tracking
- Weekly performance reports with charts

